headline: Trimble Announces Filing of Form 10-K for 2024
summary: Trimble Inc. (the "Company") (Nasdaq: TRMB) announced today that it has filed its Annual Report on Form 10-K for the year ended January 3, 2025 with the Securities and Exchange Commission. There were no changes to the Company's financial statements as presented during the earnings call held by the Company on February 19, 2025.
